snippet.title: eFootball™ Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing #eFootball™, an all-new football simulation platform from the makers of PES and Winning Eleven.

Overhauled graphics, animations and gameplay signal a new era of virtual football. Available free-to-play this Autumn.
